node.text: I thought I’d make a fun little video on my phone of making this delicious honey Focaccia and collecting the honey I used from my @flowhive . it’s a great italian flat bread crispy on the top yet deeply soft and spongy inside yum….it can easily transition breakfast, brunch & amazing filled savoury sandwiches for lunch it’s on page 12 of my new book that you can be pre ordered now it’s out in a month ! All Very exciting it’s called Together I can’t wait to share it with you happy Sunday love Jamie o xxx

node.text: A level Results Day today guys! This little munchkin my second daughter Daisy gets here A level results at 830am this morning it’s going to be a real moment just like for many other parents and students out there! Good luck….Daisy what ever grades you get today I’ll be proud of you I’ve seen how hard you’ve worked against all the odds and honestly that’s all that matters. For me as some one that really struggled and failed at school and certainly never went to university I feel there is a huge amount of pressure on young people and parents to get exactly the results you want, to get to exactly the university you want and the list goes on and on ….all I would say is today does not defined YOU getting to where YOU want to be and achieving what YOU think YOU want to achieve…. that (i think)is a long old game….try to relax if that’s possible…. If you don’t get what you want today and have that immediate gratification I’d say try to embrace the struggle, it might not be your destiny to have it easy and for good reason for I can assure you it is your struggle and the challenges you navigate in life that will define YOU and allow you thrive and be the best version of you u can be .  Try to enjoy the ride it goes fast !…if you don’t get the exam results or the uni or the halls of residence that you wanted first time don’t worry it will all work it’s self out if you really really want it, so good luck folks;  students hug your parents it’s bloody hard being an onlooker in this day and age and parents let’s have a drink at 6 pm haha you’ll need it much love and good vibes to you all jamie oxxx
